It’s been ten years since I first sculpted the TC3D “slaughterhouse mask”. That mold has been long gone and after many requests, I’ve finally started a new one. This sculpt will be finished tonight/tomorrow. The first run will be limited to ten masks to ensure that I don’t fall too far behind. Message me to get on the preorder list (9 spots remaining) #leatherface #texaschainsaw3d #texaschainsawmassacre #horror #sculpture #sfx #horrormask #halloween #halloweencostume

Virtual yard sale. Unfortunately these are the only photos I could get before the storm rolled in. These are masks that have been in storage for a while, most are $15-30. Send a message with any questions, I know it’s hard to see some of the prices. I’ve been dealing with sciatica as a result of injuring my back moving heavy molds at work so I’m having a hard time right now, and just trying to catch up on ALL back orders and clear out EVERYTHING that I’ve had sitting around. Im going to be taking a big step back from the mask business once I’m caught up, so I’m selling masters as well (a few in the final picture). Thank you all for your support and patience. #yardsale #horror #halloween #leatherface #michaelmyers #jeeperscreepers #wrongturn #jasonvoorhees #freddykrueger #nightmareonelmstreet #fridaythe13th #texaschainsawmassacre
